OL,3,C'Constant air of threat': Tensions
OL,4,Cover new migrants dividing
OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FWolverhampton is a symbol of our multi-
OL,8,Fcultural country.
OL,10,FOver the course of the past 60 years,
OL,11,Fit's been transformed by immigration.
OL,13,FAnd in the process, its people have
OL,14,Fproved the inflammatory predictions of
OL,15,Fits former MP hopelessly wrong.
OL,17,FBack in 1968, Enoch Powell foresaw
OL,18,Finter-racial strife of such violence
OL,19,Fthat he invoked the deliberately
OL,20,Fterrifying image of 'Rivers of Blood'
OL,21,Fflowing.
