OL,7,FIt was a speech that cost Powell his
OL,8,Fcareer and ` ironically ` stymied any
OL,9,Ffurther mainstream debate about
OL,10,Fimmigration.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Wolverhampton continued to
OL,13,Fabsorb newcomers, often from Britain's
OL,14,Fformer colonies, to work in its
OL,15,Ffactories and hospitals and elsewhere.
OL,17,FAnyone who grew up here in the 60s and
OL,18,F70s will remember that it hasn't
OL,19,Falways been easy.
