OL,7,FBut together, the people of
OL,8,FWolverhampton have, by and large, made
OL,9,Fit work.
OL,11,FBut, over this past year or so, we
OL,12,Fhave heard of a rise again in tensions
OL,13,Fand new questions over immigration.
OL,15,FAll that is reflected in our Ipsos
OL,16,Fpoll, which finds people anxious, and
OL,17,Fa country ill at ease, after a fresh
OL,18,Fwave of mass legal immigration and a
OL,19,Frise, apparently beyond control, in
OL,20,Fthe numbers of those arriving by small
OL,21,Fboat.
