OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FMembers of the well-established local
OL,8,FSikh community tell us the new ugly
OL,9,Fmood also shows in a series of
OL,10,Fallegedly racially motivated attacks.
OL,11,FPolice are investigating them all.
OL,13,F"There's a constant air of threat,"
OL,14,Fone community leader tells us.
OL,16,FThe issues are complex - questions of
OL,17,Fidentity and belonging ` and they are
OL,18,Fexacerbated by a cost-of-living
OL,19,Fcrisis, which means everyone feels
OL,20,Fmore vulnerable.
