OL,5,CWolverhampton
OL,7,FWolverhampton-born writer Sathnam
OL,8,FSanghera tells us the migrants of his
OL,9,Fparents' generation are not that keen
OL,10,Fto see newer arrivals.
OL,12,F"There are different things going on.
OL,13,FIf you look at our party politics,
OL,14,Fthat tells a very toxic story. If you
OL,15,Flook at social media, it looks like
OL,16,Fwe're on the brink of civil war.
OL,18,F"But if you look at the people, I
OL,19,Fthink what you've still got in Britain
OL,20,Fis the most successful multi-cultural
OL,21,Fsociety in the world."
